cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper is about improving the training of deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper specifically focuses on image classification benchmarks (cs.CV) and proposes a new normalization method (cs.AI) that is particularly effective for micro-batches (cs.NE). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) in some experiments.
